description: It's not just about providing an experience of seeing and touching animals, it's a space where you can understand the lives of other species and learn how to live with them on Earth through communication with animals.

The school has a classic and beautiful Gothic architecture, and it is one of the filming locations of the famous Korean drama "Winter Sonata". There is also a stationery store next to the school entrance that sells souvenirs related to "Winter Sonata", Hallyu star pictorials and magazines. It should be noted that if you want to enter the campus for a visit, you should avoid the weekday class hours.
